REQUIREMENTS
-------------

- Maya 2018
- MtoA 2.0.1

BINARY DISTRIBUTION
-------------------
The distribution package is a Maya module folder.

Unzip the 'modules" in any directory inside the MAYA_MODULE_PATH environment variable.

ie. for maya 2018 on Windows:

Edit or create
c:\Users\<user>\Documents\maya\2018-x64\Maya.env (or your OS equivalent)

Add this line:
MAYA_MODULE_PATH = %MAYA_MODULE_PATH%;c:\maya2018\modules
or on Linux/osX :
MAYA_MODULE_PATH = $MAYA_MODULE_PATH:/maya2018/modules

(alternatively, but unadviced, maya will search for modules in c:\Program Files\Autodesk\Maya2018\modules)

Unpack in c:\maya2018\modules
Resulting in a file :
c:\maya2018\modules\abcToA.mod
and a folder :
c:\maya2018\modules\AbcToA-2.2.1

You can now launch maya and load the plugins.

Alternatively, you can edit the .mod file and place the abcToA-2.2.1 somewhere else:
ie. change
+ AbcToA 2.2.1 .\AbcToA-2.2.1
to
+ AbcToA 2.2.1 s:\sharedModules\2013\AbcToA-2.2.1
